OL,3,CEisteddfod 2024 at Pontypridd: Travel
OL,4,Cadvice, parking details and ticket
OL,5,Cprices
OL,7,FThe National Eisteddfod will kick off
OL,8,Fthis Saturday, 3 August, as tens of
OL,9,Fthousands of people are expected to
OL,10,Fflock to Pontypridd.
OL,12,FThe week-long festival changes
OL,13,Flocation yearly, with 2024's event
OL,14,Ftaking place in Rhondda Cynon Taf.
OL,16,FHere's what you need to know if you're
OL,17,Fheading to the Eisteddfod:
