OL,3,CEisteddfod 2024 at Pontypridd: Travel
OL,4,Cadvice, parking details and ticket
OL,5,Cprices
OL,7,FThe National Eisteddfod is said to be
OL,8,Fthe largest cultural festival of its
OL,9,Fkind in Europe and offers a stage for
OL,10,Fpeople across the country to showcase
OL,11,Ftheir talents through the Welsh
OL,12,Flanguage.
OL,14,FIt is also a chance to enjoy cultural
OL,15,Fevents and performances; from music to
OL,16,Fdance to writing. It showcases Welsh
OL,17,Farts and promotes the use and practice
OL,18,Fof the Welsh language.
