OL,4,Cadvice, parking details and ticket
OL,5,Cprices
OL,7,FThe main events are held on the Maes,
OL,8,Fhowever gigs will also take place in a
OL,9,Fnumber of local venues.
OL,11,FMaes B, described as "the official
OL,12,Fafterdark little brother of the
OL,13,FEisteddfod", featuring "late night
OL,14,Fperformances by over 30 of the main
OL,15,FWelsh language bands, artists and
OL,16,FDJs", will be held on the outskirts of
OL,17,FPontypridd.
