OL,3,CEisteddfod 2024 at Pontypridd: Travel
OL,4,Cadvice, parking details and ticket
OL,5,Cprices
OL,7,FTypically, the Eisteddfod is held in
OL,8,Fmore rural areas, but this year the
OL,9,Fsite will be at the heart of
OL,10,FPontypridd town, in the Ynysangharad
OL,11,FWar Memorial Park.
OL,13,FThe site, referred to as the 'Maes',
OL,14,Fhas strong ties to the Welsh language
OL,15,Fas it is where the iconic Hen Wlad Fy
OL,16,FNhadau anthem was written and composed
OL,17,Falmost 200 years ago.
