OL,3,CEisteddfod 2024 at Pontypridd: Travel
OL,4,Cadvice, parking details and ticket
OL,5,Cprices
OL,7,FTransport for Wales said it is
OL,8,F"working closely with the Eisteddfod
OL,9,Fand the local council to ensure that
OL,10,Fyou can plan your journey and have the
OL,11,Foption to leave the car at home."
OL,13,FSo here's what you need to know if
OL,14,Fyou're travelling by:
OL,16,FTransport for Wales' website states
OL,17,Fthat "within the South Wales metro
OL,18,Farea", they are "providing additional
OL,19,Ftrains during the Eisteddfod event to
OL,20,Ftravel from Cardiff to Pontypridd
OL,21,Funtil the event finishes each evening".
