OL,3,CEisteddfod 2024 at Pontypridd: Travel
OL,4,Cadvice, parking details and ticket
OL,5,Cprices
OL,7,FPontypridd railway station is a five-
OL,8,Fminute walk to/from the Maes and a 25-
OL,9,Fminute walk to/from Maes B.
OL,11,FYou can take a direct train from
OL,12,FCardiff Central to Merthyr Tydfil,
OL,13,FAberdare and Treherbert as they all
OL,14,Fstop in Pontypridd.
OL,16,FIf you are travelling from the
OL,17,Fdirections of Bridgend, Barry Island,
OL,18,FPenarth or Rhymney, you will need to
OL,19,Fchange trains at Cardiff Queen Street
OL,20,For Cardiff Central to reach Pontypridd.
