OL,4,Cadvice, parking details and ticket
OL,5,Cprices
OL,7,FFrom Cardiff Bay or Cardiff Queen
OL,8,FStreet, you can also use the new
OL,9,FCardiff Bay to Pontypridd service.
OL,10,FTreforest and Trehafod railway
OL,11,Fstations are also nearby.
OL,13,FTravellers should be aware that
OL,14,Fstations are expected to be busy
OL,15,Fduring the event, especially through
OL,16,FCardiff on the weekend of August 9
OL,17,Fwhen there is a stadium concert in the
OL,18,Fcity.
