OL,3,CEisteddfod 2024 at Pontypridd: Travel
OL,4,Cadvice, parking details and ticket
OL,5,Cprices
OL,7,FThere will be two park and ride sites
OL,8,F(north and south of Pontypridd) which
OL,9,Fwill be open from Saturday, 3 August,
OL,10,Fto Saturday, 10 August.
OL,12,FThey will run frequently, and for
OL,13,Ffree, from 7am to midnight between the
OL,14,Fcar parks and the Maes.
OL,16,FAs there is no event parking near the
OL,17,FMaes, organisers are encouraging those
OL,18,Fwith cars to use the free park and
OL,19,Fride services. There is no event
OL,20,Fparking near the Maes, except disabled
OL,21,Fparking.
