OL,3,CEisteddfod 2024 at Pontypridd: Travel
OL,4,Cadvice, parking details and ticket
OL,5,Cprices
OL,7,FEvent-goers have been warned that
OL,8,Froads are expected to be much busier
OL,9,Fthan usual during the week.
OL,11,FBecause of this, it is strongly
OL,12,Fadvised that people avoid driving into
OL,13,Fthe town centre.
OL,15,FAccessibility
OL,17,FThere will be limited disabled parking
OL,18,Favailable at Catherine Street Car Park
OL,19,F(CF37 2TB).
