OL,3,CEisteddfod 2024 at Pontypridd: Travel
OL,4,Cadvice, parking details and ticket
OL,5,Cprices
OL,7,FThis will be managed by the Eisteddfod
OL,8,Fand access will be restricted to those
OL,9,Fwith a blue badge.
OL,11,FTransport for Wales added: "Those with
OL,12,Frestricted mobility arriving by car
OL,13,Fare advised to use Park and Ride North
OL,14,F(Abercynon) where a low-floor vehicle
OL,15,Fwill transfer you to the festival."
OL,17,FTickets will be available to purchase
OL,18,Fat the Maes, as well as on the
OL,19,FEisteddfod's website.
